metadata.name: AI Mutant PFP #001
metadata.description: I AM AN AI MUTANT PFPs! Unique NFT art for the heart, the eye and the soul. I have come a long way from being born as a sketch, randomized into an unique generated base image and heavily beaten by the AI in different art styles. Thousands and thousands of other mutants have been generated, curated and deleted. Just a handful have survived. I am one strong survivor of mutation, an artistic fighters for art and sensual expressions of your inner soul. I am here to show you what I am and what you are. MUTANTS!
